# Keystores (never commit signing material)
*.jks
*.keystore
keystore.properties
# Belt-and-suspenders: also ignore anything that looks like the Play
# Store release keystore by name, in case someone copies it into the
# repo by mistake. The real file lives OUTSIDE the repo (default
# location: ~/.storyvox-keystore/storyvox-release.keystore) and is
# wired in via `storyvox.releaseStoreFile` in local.properties.
# See docs/release-keystore.md.
storyvox-release.keystore
storyvox-upload.keystore
# …except the debug-only keystore used for sideload installs. Stable
# cert across CI + dev machines so APKs install over each other
# without "package conflicts" errors. No security value, intentional.
!app/storyvox-debug.keystore

# storyvox-local
.superpowers/
.claude/
scratch/

# Issue #417 — :source-kvmr was renamed to :source-radio. Older
# checkouts of the repo still write build artifacts into
# source-kvmr/build/ when their settings.gradle.kts still includes
# `:source-kvmr`; ignoring the entire directory keeps those orphan
# trees from creeping into commits via `git add .` or IDE plugins.
# See issue #696.
source-kvmr/

# Misc
*.bak
*.swp
